infovis.column
Class ColumnId

java.lang.Object
  infovis.column.AbstractColumn
      infovis.column.ColumnProxy
          infovis.column.ColumnId
All Implemented Interfaces:
ChangeListener, Column, Constants, EventListener, cern.colt.function.IntComparator, Metadata, NumberColumn, RowComparator, Serializable
public class ColumnId
extends ColumnProxy
implements NumberColumn

Class ColumnId wraps any column to make it a NumberColumn. As value, it simply returns the index of the element.
